fields.title: Welcome to MESCO
fields.subtitle: Helping people live better tomorrow
fields.content:
MESCO is a Secular Trust registered in 1968 with the Charity Commissioner of Mumbai. The organization is a selfless effort for serving mankind which began with a few friends who constituted the first Managing Committee. 'Education' was identified as a core theme for human development by the organization and later it expanded to provide Medical Assistance and Poverty Relief.

The organization touches the lives of over 15,000 families annually through a combination of well strategized and implemented schemes, programs, activities and its institutions. The approach has always been to uphold ethical values in delivering and becoming a channel to deliver resources from those who want to give to those who need it the most. Trusted today by a large number of noble souls (individuals, families, foundations, charities and corporate) both in the country and abroad, the organization strives to bring happiness...
